=== Midodrine

α1-adrenergic agonist that constricts peripheral veins and arterioles. Probes venous pooling or inadequate vasoconstriction. ==== If midodrine works

peripheral vasoconstriction was insufficient. More likely with connective tissue laxity or autonomic neuropathy. *Combination:* midodrine + pyridostigmine superior to monotherapy (meta-analysis @Pavic2025pyridostigmine).

*Certainty*   Medium.

*Level of action*   Symptom management.